title: ALRT
description:
ALRT the Israeli fast-rising force in the hard dance scene, best known for his heavy-hitting sound mixing elements of hardstyle, dubstep, trap and old-school rave makes his SF debut!

The DIRTY NOT SORRY crew hosts with support sets from JAXX T B2B KNIVES, LUCO B2B SPRACTO + DREAMSHADOW B2B YESNOYES!

This is a 21+ event
